Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:50.00,名单,,0,0,0,,翻译：慕斯 柯小南 呆毛 elsa 肉丝 vera强妹 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:01:00.00,名单,,0,0,0,,校对：柯小南
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:10.00,名单,,0,0,0,,后期：hhjie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:20.00,名单,,0,0,0,,时间轴：阿黎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:30.00,名单,,0,0,0,,总监：柯小南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:02.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,塞勒姆前情回顾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Previously on "Salem"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,女巫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:07.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在塞勒姆还从没有女人有那种权力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No woman in Salem has ever had that kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:09.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,即使是玛丽 西布利也没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not even Mary Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:11.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那屋子的女主人是我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The lady of the house is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:14.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们已经发现了一个巫师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We've uncovered a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:17.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这回您会在镇上呆多久\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How long may we enjoy your curative presence in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:22.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一直到塞勒姆镇最后一个卖身魔鬼的女巫死光\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Until every last Devil's whore of a witch in Salem is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:25.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柏翠的巫术只能维持一天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Petrus' physic will last but a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:27.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后 西布利会醒来 神志清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and then Mr. Sibley will awake, lucid and eager.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:30.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,会亟不可待地告诉因科瑞斯一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To tell Increase everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:55.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,选一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Choose one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:00.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,喝吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:03.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,享受的喝下去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Drink and... Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:07.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只有凡人易受俗物的诱惑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Only mere mortals are vulnerable to man-made spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:10.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,作为人类来说 你真的很令人憎恶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}As a man, you are an abomination,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:13.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但你还不是巫师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but you are no witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:19.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在你可以和你那个令人可怜的软弱 一起滚开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now begone with you and your... Pitiful weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.63,0:01:30.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,该起床了 我的好夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Time to wake, my good madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:02:00.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让他们不能再说 上帝会安排一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let them no more say, "God must do all,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:03.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,以此来教唆他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and so encourage themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:09.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,从此远离上帝 也远离内心的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to live in a careless neglect of God and of their own souls
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:12.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,救赎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and salvation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:19.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,魔鬼已经把这个村庄搞得不成样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The Devil has made a dreadful knot of witches in the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:21.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,并且在巫师的帮助下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and, by the help of witches,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:25.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,变本加厉的继续破坏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}has dreadfully Increased that knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:36.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,孩子们啊 提高一些警惕吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, children, children, be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:41.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,睡觉前一定要祈祷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and go not prayerless to your bed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:44.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这样才不会做噩梦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}lest the Devil be your bedfellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,早上好  牧师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good morning, Reverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布里夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mrs. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,要一起吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:36.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,您对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There are no words
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:38.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我丈夫的再造之恩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to encompass my overwhelming gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的感激难以言表\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}at your reclamation of my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果不是您在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}When I think what might have transpired
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-后果真的难以想象 -是么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}had you not been there  -Indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那究竟会有什么后果呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Exactly what might have transpired?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:47.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-什么  -我的意思是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Excuse me? -  Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:52.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你家的女仆难道不会直接送他去医院吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Would not your slave girl simply have taken him on to hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没错 不就是你派她去救他嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, it was you who sent her to his rescue,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我一听说立马就派她去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Once I'd heard of the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不过 我还是很困惑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am perplexed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:08.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我 你为什么这么着急想要把乔治秘密带出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell me, why was George scurried off with such haste and secrecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:12.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他经常去波士顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He goes often to Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:14.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-去看病  -他没生病\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- His illness... - He's not ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:17.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-他是被下蛊了 -他没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's spelled. Mary: No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:18.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:19.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好好想想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Consider...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:24.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,乔治是不是无缘无故的病了好多年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}has not George suffered this mysterious malady
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,病了好多年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}without explication for several years now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:31.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而且没有一个医生能说出病因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and have not the doctors expressed utter befuddlement
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说出病因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}as to its cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-没错 但是 -是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, but... - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这样说来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In such cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,答案就显而易见了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the answer is oft the simplest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,乔治没有生病\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}George is not ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:43.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他是被邪恶的魔鬼控制了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He is under the influence of the Devil's darkest tool...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是巫师的咒语\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a witch's spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:49.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而且下周的人似乎与她非常亲近\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And it is quite likely that this speller resides close at hearth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:57.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许就在你家的某个地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Perhaps even in the hallowed halls of your own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,控告\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:06.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你一定忍了很久了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It dances on your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我确信你误会我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, I assure you, you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在我想立刻把我的丈夫接回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then I wish to bring my husband home immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不能这样做 西布利夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think not, Mrs. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你有什么权利拒绝我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You would deny me that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在找到施咒者之前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I must deny you that right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不得不拒绝你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}until we can discover the origin of the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:28.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:33.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那我坚持\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then I would ask, or, rather, insist,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:36.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,需要有人照顾西布利先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that someone attend to Mr. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:39.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,最好是有这种经验的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Someone who has experience with his travails.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那个年轻人怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What about that young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就是那个在他去波士顿的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the one who was to take him to Boston, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:46.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-以撒么 -没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Isaac? -  Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Isaac will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他还在昏迷吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He sleeps still?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有侍卫在看守他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Under the care of sentries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对了  玛丽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, and, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你大可放心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Be of good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:05.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,酒吧老板兰姆先生说他可能随时醒来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mr. Lamb, the barkeep, tells me that he may wake at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:13.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cotton.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:24.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,除了心还在跳以外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No difference between me and those that already rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我和那些死人没什么区别\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Besides a still-beating heart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:28.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在我只是一个有灵魂的空壳罢了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in a shell where my soul no longer resides.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:41.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,早上好 牧师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good morning, Reverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我在想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I Wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要怎样才能重新站起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}what would it take to get you to your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:49.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么这样想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why would you wish to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我害怕我可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I fear I may have...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:01.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,以前对你的评判太毫不留情了 麦哲教士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Judged you too harshly, Reverend Mather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:05.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,直到现在 当我已经远离童年的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It is only now, when leaving my childhood behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:08.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我才意识到 我们无论是现在还是将来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that I realize we are, past and forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都是父亲的孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}our fathers' children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:12.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们不能控制他们是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And we can no more control who they be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,和他们是怎样影响我们的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and how they came to form us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:17.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果那样的话我们都能操纵太阳的东升西落了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}then we can the rise and setting of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:22.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对于你爱的女孩我感到很抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am sorry about your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们能送你回家吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}May we see you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,起来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:50.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,等他安定下来了 上尉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Once he's settled, captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:52.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我能请你帮个忙吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}may I ask a favor of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不这么认为 西布利女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}"I think not, Mrs. Sibley."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说得好像他是苏格拉底 而我只是他膝下学生一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}As if he were socrates and I, a student at his knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让我杀了他吧 可以吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let me kill him, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让我为你减轻这个负担吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let me ease this burden for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-就像我对其他事情那样 -玛丽：英克瑞斯 麦哲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- as I've done the others. - Mary: Increase Mather is known
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是全世界家喻户晓的人物 老少皆知\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}throughout the world, new and old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他的失踪或死亡不能轻描淡写的对待\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}His disappearance or death will not be taken lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:12.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他的项上人头不能放在任何一个人的木盘里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}His head will sit on no man's platter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他可比不上你 这是一定的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's no match for you, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是你做错的地方 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That is where you are wrong, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:18.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真正的考验就是让我们与势均力敌的人战斗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is our truest test To battle equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rev. Lewis: Mrs. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:23.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,牧师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Reverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,黙茜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想知道 我可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rev. Lewis: I wonder if I might have a private word
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:29.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,和我的女儿私下里说几句吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:31.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得不行 牧师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think not, Reverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我 -玛丽：把艾萨克带来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I... -Mary: Fetch me Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我是 呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rev. Lewis: I am, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:45.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为你对我女儿的仁慈感到惊讶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Astounded at the charity you've shown my child,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:50.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但如果我想要见她 这难道不是一个父亲的权利吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but if I wish to see her, is that not a father's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:53.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么 偏偏想要见她 牧师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why, in particular, do you wish to see her, Reverend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:57.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还在考虑另一个驱魔仪式吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Were you perhaps considering another exorcism?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的日子难道会日渐无趣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do your days grow dull,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,缺少了这个孩子给你鞭打虐待\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}lacking a child to beat and torture
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:03.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,少了一个可以拜访的女儿 夜晚也会变得孤独吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and the nights far too lonely with no daughter to visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:06.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-路易斯牧师：我永远不会 -玛丽：默茜是我的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Rev. Lewis: I would never... - Mary: Mercy is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:09.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你再到这里一次 我就会公开指控你的这些罪行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Return here again and these accusations will be made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:25.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利大人怎么样了 他醒了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What of master Sibley? Has he woken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:28.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,长老会的人不能再等了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The elders will wait no longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:31.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们需要你带着观众去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They require an audience with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他醒了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Has he woken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:00.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,任何时候都行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Any moment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这只是个意外 女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It were an accident, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:15.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在路上有一个绊脚的木材\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A wayward timber in the path,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:18.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,结果我们六七点钟才醒过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and we found ourselves at sixes and sevens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没关系 艾萨克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's okay, Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:21.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你已经尽力了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know you've done your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:22.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,牧师在叫我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The Reverend summons me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:25.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,天知道是为什么 但我害怕再让他多等一秒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}heaven knows why, but I fear each second he's made to wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:27.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他会让你看着西不里先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He will ask you to watch over Mr. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:31.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他会吗 -玛丽：在我的坚持下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He will? - Mary: At my grave insistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,既然他已经拒绝了我的愿望\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}since he refuses my desire
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不让我把我的丈夫带回家好好照顾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to bring my husband home to proper care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他拒绝了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He refuses you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:41.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,塞勒姆镇像是一个笨拙的陀螺一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Salem reels out of control like an unwieldy spin top
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在英克瑞斯 麦哲的小聪明的带领下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}at the whim of Increase Mather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:47.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一种药 施加睡眠的痛苦与放松\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A tonic... the pain and ease of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,艾萨克 我求求你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Isaac, I beseech you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在这件秘密而又重要的事情上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in this most private and important matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,完成我做不到的恳求\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}do my bidding where I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,立刻给他下药并且让他一直沉睡下去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Dose him immediately and keep him so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,乔治不应该被强迫着承受\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}George should not be made to suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:01.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,老麦哲毫无根据的怀疑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for Mather senior's unfounded suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他 他不应该\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}H-he shall not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:11.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,艾萨克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And Isaac...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:15.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,记得保密\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:17.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就像是塞勒姆镇的许多秘密一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Like so many of Salem's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,保密\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-英克瑞斯：你知道吗 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Increase: Are you aware, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:31.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的故事在这块土地上已经传了很远 臭名昭著\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your story is known far and wide throughout the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:34.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,私通者艾萨克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Isaac the fornicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:38.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不要羞耻的低下你的头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, no, no. Do not bow your head in shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:40.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抬头 昂起你的头颅\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Head up. Get your head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抬头 抬头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Head up. Head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:47.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,私通者艾萨克的故事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The story of Isaac the fornicator
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:49.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是神圣的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}is a holy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:53.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们清教徒把它当做一个活着的先例\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It is used as a living precedent by we puritans
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:58.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来向我们的孩子讲述诱惑的邪恶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to illustrate to the children the evils of lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:01.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 不 你的罪与罚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, no. Your sin and your suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:06.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,被转化成了伟大而又神圣的祝福\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}it has been transformed into a great and a holy blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为 我的孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For, my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你感受到了上帝之手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You felt the hand of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他触摸了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's touched you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他在改变你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's working through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:23.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他选中了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's chosen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:24.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:28.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有多少人能说自己是被上帝选中的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How many can say that they have been chosen by God?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,被选中来做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Chosen for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:38.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,孩子 你有没有想过除了塞勒姆之外的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Son, have you ever imagined a world beyond Salem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-嗯 -我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Hmm? -I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抬起头来 抬起你的头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Get your head up, your head up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:44.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抬起来 抬起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}your head up, your head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,先生 我在这活得很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have a good life here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:50.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为西布利夫人做些琐碎的杂事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, performing meager errands for Mrs. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:53.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她对我一直很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She's been good to me. Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她的慈善让你站在她的那一方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her charity binds you to her bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:59.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不不不不 以撒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. No, no, no, Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在这之外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,孩子 在这以外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Out there, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,世界这么大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's a vast world out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:12.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,机遇这么多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}full of... full of opportunities,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:16.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只要你抬起头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and if you... if you would walk the straight road
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,沿着这街走下去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in the sunlight with your head up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我会带着你去看的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I would take you with me to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:23.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:25.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想要吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Would you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What would I have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:30.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:32.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要做的是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You will have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:34.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,站在西布利先生这一边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}have to tend to Mr. Sibley there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要做的是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You'll have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:39.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,确保他的安全和健康\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Make certain that he is fresh and tidy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:43.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要知道 这并不容易\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and that is no easy task, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:48.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,最重要的是 他一醒来你就要告知于我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Most importantly, you must alert me the moment that he wakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:51.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:00.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你可以么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can you do that, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:03.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我能问一下么 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you mind me asking, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这些是干嘛的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}what these are for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:11.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,帮助西布利先生抵抗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Protection for Mr. Sibley against...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,外界的阻力的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Outer forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这些都是一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's cremated ash...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:21.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,200岁女巫的骨灰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Of a 200-year-old witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:22.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有 以撒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And, Isaac...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我亲手烧了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I burned her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:34.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,房顶 这里和这里 要修补\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So, the roof needs patching there and there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:36.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,新涂的这层油漆不会坏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a fresh coat of paint wouldn't hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还需要四到五个床给这些小一点的孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}nor would four or five more beds for the smaller children,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:41.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我吓到你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and... I'm overwhelming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:42.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没 没\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我渴望将我的精力都付出\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm eager to put my energies to good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,船长 这些孩子都吓到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The children are frightened, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:59.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,被今天的这个悬尸还有未知的死亡吓到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Another hung today and not an inkling who's to be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们都不知道哪一个更令人害怕了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They're unsure who to fear more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,女巫还是追捕他们的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}witches or those who pursue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:07.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那 谁能指责他们呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, who can blame them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他不和别人一起玩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He doesn't play with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那个深色头发的男孩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The dark-haired boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:17.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他在这已经两年了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's been here two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他的父母被印度人杀了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}His parents were murdered by Indians.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:23.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们说他全看见了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They say he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有人知道他怎么活下来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No one knows how he survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:29.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有人问过么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Has anyone asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他从不说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He doesn't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:34.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,至少 自从那时起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}At least, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:38.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就再也不说话了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not since... Then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道如何补屋顶么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you know anything about patching a roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mrs. Sibley?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她不在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The mistress is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:07.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要和她说的也可以和我说说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Anything needed to be said to her can be said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢  真可爱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, that's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的仆人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,仆人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:29.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,魔鬼赠与的礼物用来执行我的命令的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A gift from the Devil to do my bidding,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:31.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的精神伴侣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}my spiritual companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是她怎么吃东西的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is how she feeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我会有一个仆人么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Will I get a familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,假以时日\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我该如何选择\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How do I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不要选的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,它选择你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It chooses you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:31.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利夫人 你好啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good day, Mrs. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,孩子们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们去墓地见默茜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We're off to meet Mercy in the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那去吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}On your way, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们对她的损失都很遗憾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We all grieve the loss of our sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:29.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我承认\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I do not argue this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:33.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但要记住 我没得选择\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But beg remembrance that I was given little choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,潘多拉之盒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The malum...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:42.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是这个仪式不可或缺的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Without which our grand rite would not be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:57.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,露丝把它带到这 要使用这死亡的工具\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rose brought it here, this instrument of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:20:01.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有我的学识 来挑战我打败我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}without my knowledge, to challenge and defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:19.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是给你们的 为我们的事业承受报复的代价\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It is for you, retrieved at great cost,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:23.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,放弃爱和热情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}relinquished with love and ardor for our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只给你们留下这世间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I leave you now with the only tool
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:28.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,唯一可以控制我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that exists on earth to control me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:55.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,诀窍就是劈开它们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The trick to making shakes is to split them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:59.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是砍 不是锯 而是劈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}not chopped or sawed, but to split.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:01.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:10.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,换你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:18.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对 就这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Right! Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:20.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:23.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mrs. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:26.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,小伙子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:30.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你去看看那边有没有清水\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why don't you go see if there's any fresh water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么风把你刮来啦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Big doings this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:41.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,惊喜天天见 没什么稀罕的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Seems every day brings its fair share of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听说老英克瑞斯抓了你丈夫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I heard old Increase took possession of your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:44.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很想把他救回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I'm eager to get him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真假的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:51.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:55.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这很奇怪么 上尉先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is it so unusual, Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一个妻子想要丈夫回家这很正常啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for a wife to want her husband at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:01.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,大多数情况下的确很正常\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In most cases, it's not unusual at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:05.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听说我辛苦干活的老公口渴啦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I heard my hard worker was thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:07.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 西布利夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, Mrs. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:08.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,额 这里有新鲜的苹果汁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh, fresh apple water on offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不了 谢谢你 安妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, thank you, Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:13.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,再见了 上尉 小伙子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good day, Captain. Young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:19.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:50.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我可以吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:27.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-先生好  -你好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sir. - Man: Good morrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.45,0:23:33.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要是想要对你的弱点屈服\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If you're going to capitulate to your weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:37.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,非要这样公之于众吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}must it be on constant public display?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:42.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那让你来公之于众怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Shall I leave public display to you, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.09,0:23:43.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们应当废了绞刑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Shall we abolish the noose
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:46.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好让你用自己的双手拧断自己的脖子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}so that you may break necks with your own two hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.66,0:23:49.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她之前就死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.76,0:23:53.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那个妓女走私者是自杀的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The whore runner killed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.60,0:23:56.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她既然已经死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She was already dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:57.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还把她上绞刑吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and yet you hung her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:23:59.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我说了她会被绞死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I said she would hang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.68,0:24:01.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她就得给我绞死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And hang she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:04.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,人无信 无以立\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We are nothing if we do not keep our word,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:09.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,恐怕你还不明白这个道理吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a principle which seems to mean very little to you, I fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:13.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你真的要这么恨我吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Must you hate me so?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 柯顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, Cotton.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.36,0:24:21.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你母亲也叫柯顿 这你是知道的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your mother was a Cotton, as you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.43,0:24:24.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她是我的异父的妹妹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And my stepsister.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.04,0:24:27.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们的婚姻是历史必然的结果\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Our marriage was a historical inevitability.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.74,0:24:29.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,柯顿家族和麦哲家族\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The cottons and the Mathers...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.75,0:24:31.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谁能抵挡的了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}who could resist such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.62,0:24:35.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如此权力和声望的结合\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}such a joining of... of power and prestige?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.69,0:24:38.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你肯定不能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Certainly not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.39,0:24:41.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她是个好女人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She was a good woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.36,0:24:44.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是个合格的母亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and she was a fit enough mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.03,0:24:47.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.46,0:24:49.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我并不爱她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I didn't love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.63,0:24:54.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道爱为何物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I didn't love.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.74,0:24:57.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,于是 你诞生了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And then you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.94,0:25:02.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,成了现在这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And there you were, a...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.31,0:25:07.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哭哭啼啼的一团废物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Squalling mess of limbs and of hair, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.71,0:25:10.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你成不了大器\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You weren't much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.82,0:25:13.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不过你让我知道了爱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But you were enough to show me love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.66,0:25:20.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这可真特么讽刺啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What utter irony
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.70,0:25:25.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你将从我这里遗传到同样的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that you would then take the self-same thing from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.57,0:25:27.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Henry: Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.11,0:25:29.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,先生 你没钱了 我们不卖给你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are cut off, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.21,0:25:31.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我有钱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. I have money!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.95,0:25:34.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还可以喝喝喝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I will drink muchly and often!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.68,0:25:36.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不会 给我滚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You will not. Now be on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.55,0:25:39.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-谁说的 -哦 不不 滚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think not. - Lamb: Oh, no, no. Whoa. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.69,0:25:48.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,美酒来自上帝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The wine is from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.80,0:25:52.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,酒鬼来自地狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The drunkard is from the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.41,0:26:07.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,振作起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.34,0:26:09.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,路还远着呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's much work to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.59,0:26:20.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让我杀了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let me kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.82,0:26:22.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.19,0:26:24.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们不能杀英克瑞斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We cannot kill Increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.23,0:26:26.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我说的不是又老又蠢的老英克瑞斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not silly old Increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.26,0:26:27.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mr. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.57,0:26:29.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你就是这样教她的么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is what you teach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.10,0:26:33.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,遇到问题第一个想的办法居然是谋杀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For any problem, murder is the first course of action?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.21,0:26:36.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们不能杀乔治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We cannot kill George.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.21,0:26:38.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为何不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.04,0:26:41.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,您一个人的力量就已经非常强大了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You are so powerful You alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.55,0:26:44.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不需要他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- You do not need him. - Mary:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.32,0:26:46.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你错就错在这里 亲爱的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That is where you are wrong, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.45,0:26:48.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们非常需要他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We need him desperately.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.92,0:26:51.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有了乔治 就等于没有了一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Without George, it all goes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.69,0:26:53.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我就成了一个一无所有的寡妇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am a widow with nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.66,0:26:57.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有生意可做 在市镇委员中也没有发言权\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}no business to run, no voice with the selectmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.47,0:27:00.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只要他活着 我就可以通过他说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}With him alive, I can speak through him...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.07,0:27:03.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让他成为一个被操控意志和思想的木偶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a puppet to parrot his wishes and thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.10,0:27:08.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是 一旦他死了他就没用了 而我也将一点权力也没有了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But dead, he is useless and I am without power.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.04,0:27:10.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不过你如何让他不说话呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But how will you stop him from speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.58,0:27:13.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我会进入他的头脑 从里面毁灭一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I will enter his mind and destroy it from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.55,0:27:16.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他的肉身会活着 不过意志将会死去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}His body will live on, but his mind will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.25,0:27:17.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你怎么能做到呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How will you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.45,0:27:19.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,闭嘴吧 你问的太多了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Quiet girl! That is enough questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.96,0:27:21.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你别想让我安静\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't you tell me to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.29,0:27:23.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-闭嘴 -够了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Quiet. - Mary: Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.29,0:27:25.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们两个给我出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Both of you, leave me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.73,0:27:27.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-但是我可以帮你啊 -滚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But I can help you. - Mary: Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.24,0:27:34.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.38,0:27:36.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-嘘 -给我放开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Shh! - Mercy: Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.21,0:27:38.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道我们会杀谁吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know who we could kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.02,0:27:39.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.15,0:27:41.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你敢 她不会让你得逞的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You can't. She would never let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.39,0:27:43.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许会 也许不会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.72,0:27:46.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不会想知道的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You don't want to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.26,0:27:49.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你这个自私狠毒卑鄙的女人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're jealous and spiteful and awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.93,0:27:53.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我等了好多好多年了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Years... I have waited many, many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.90,0:27:56.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,给我滚远远儿的 你个贱人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stay out of my way, you little bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.35,0:28:09.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利夫人一直细心照料你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mrs. Sibley's only ever had your best interest at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.19,0:28:14.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yet still...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.06,0:28:16.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在你最绝望的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your moment's worst desperation,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.26,0:28:18.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你喊的居然不是她的名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}it was not her name you uttered for rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.56,0:28:21.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,却是老教父麦哲的名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but that of the Reverend Mather senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.43,0:28:25.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你说我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do I,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.00,0:28:29.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这么了解你的心狠手辣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}who have known only violence and malice from your eager hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.58,0:28:33.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么会在乎你被折磨成什么样子呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}care a whit about your rosy outlook?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.55,0:29:03.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.65,0:29:06.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.79,0:29:14.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,终于拜托了你的控制\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Free of your precious familiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.23,0:29:16.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我终于可以自由的做梦了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I finally got hold of my dreams back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.19,0:29:18.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 对你这如此黑暗扭曲的心灵来说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hmm. A beatific choice
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.23,0:29:20.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,未尝不是个美好的选择呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for such a dark and twisted mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.83,0:29:24.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你记得我们来过这儿吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You remember coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.36,0:29:27.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,记得 来这野餐过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes. A picnic. - George:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.50,0:29:30.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,唯独这天我几乎没有鄙视你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The one and only day I almost didn't despise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.90,0:29:32.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你从来没给过我机会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You never gave me a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.67,0:29:34.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你心意已决\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your mind was long made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.80,0:29:36.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这能怪我吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can you blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.71,0:29:38.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你偷走了我的人生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You stole my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.64,0:29:40.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在你也偷走了我的人生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And now you've stolen mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.21,0:29:41.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们离得很近\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.98,0:29:44.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,非常近\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.25,0:29:47.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,盛大的仪式马上就要完成了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The grand rite is almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.35,0:29:48.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,接下来呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.55,0:29:50.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去统治另一个国家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Another kingdom for you to rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.38,0:29:51.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.92,0:29:54.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一个我不再需要你的国度\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A world in which I no longer need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.52,0:29:57.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一个你终于死去的美好国度\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A blessed world in which you can finally die.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.55,0:29:58.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是威胁挑衅的节奏啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Peril and threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.79,0:30:00.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,四面楚歌  成王败寇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Many a union has relied on less.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.99,0:30:03.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不要这么害怕啊 乔治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't look so worried, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.83,0:30:06.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们还有点路要走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We're a little ways off yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.33,0:30:08.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在 我只需要你给我闭上嘴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For now, I just need you quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.80,0:30:14.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,像天使一般 睡在你肮脏的尿布里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}sleeping like an angel in your dirty bibs and nappies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.46,0:30:37.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,永别了 乔治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Farewell, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.83,0:30:44.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你个贱人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.20,0:30:46.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,贱人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.03,0:31:01.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 那个混蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, that bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.39,0:31:03.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-西布利 -英克瑞斯 麦哲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sibley? - Mary: Increase Mather.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.80,0:31:07.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他也在场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.20,0:31:09.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,保护着乔治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Protecting George.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.12,0:31:13.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在梦里也在捍卫乔治的灵魂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Guarding his mind even in sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.66,0:31:16.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们还有个问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We have another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.23,0:31:18.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须处理一下那个女孩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We must do something about the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.84,0:31:20.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,黙茜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.17,0:31:22.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她可不可靠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She is... Unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.45,0:31:24.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,到我们无法控制她现在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It is only a matter of time before
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.42,0:31:25.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只是时间问题了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we can no longer control her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.92,0:31:28.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,像这个时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}At a time such as this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.42,0:31:31.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我比任何时候都有可能被发现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}when I am nearer to discovery and annihilation
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.32,0:31:32.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后被铲除掉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}than ever before,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.42,0:31:34.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你却因为嫉妒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you would distract yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.02,0:31:36.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,和那些恶意重伤让自己分心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}with petty jealousy and spiteful accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.89,0:31:37.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我试着要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am trying to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.99,0:31:40.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我现在真的比任何时候都需要你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Never have I needed you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.29,0:31:42.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是我却比任何时候都对你感到失望\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And never have you disappointed me so gravely.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.70,0:31:45.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我愿意为你做一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I would do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.13,0:31:46.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.20,0:31:48.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 我倒喜欢你不爱我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, and I wish to God you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.93,0:31:52.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爱我少一点 也许会更好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Love me less and you will love me better.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.44,0:31:54.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,想办法接近乔治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Find a way to get to George.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.58,0:32:01.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,明天我们将会喷漆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tomorrow, we'll work on the paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.41,0:32:04.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当然如果你还有空的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That is, if you're still available, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.02,0:32:05.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,漂亮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.59,0:32:08.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Excellent, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.03,0:32:14.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.96,0:32:18.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.20,0:32:20.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你见过我的女儿的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You've seen my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.04,0:32:24.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你可以走了  这里只有孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You can move along. There's kids here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.14,0:32:26.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我就是在找一个孩子  我的孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm looking for a kid... my kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.51,0:32:28.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而我也说了 快滚吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I said, "Move along."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.54,0:32:30.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,霍普金斯先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mr. Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.41,0:32:32.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有什么可以帮你的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How can we help you?
