Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.69,0:39:02.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不会走的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.86,0:39:07.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不会的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I won't. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.00,0:39:10.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,求你别打了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.05,0:39:20.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,亨利 霍普金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Henry Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.71,0:39:40.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这都是些什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.74,0:40:06.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,斯戴芬\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.57,0:40:09.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那个男孩的名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's his name, the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.17,0:40:10.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他告诉你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.54,0:40:12.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.84,0:40:15.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他两年都没说话了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Two years without speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.38,0:40:17.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你陪了他一天 他就告诉你他的名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and in one day, he tells you his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.75,0:40:20.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他肯定很喜欢你 上尉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He must have really taken to you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.75,0:40:22.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我不这么认为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.42,0:40:24.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我又能说什么呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And who could blame him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.49,0:40:28.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,男孩子需要关注\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Boys need attention
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.49,0:40:31.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,需要体力活消耗过剩的体能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and hard work to burn off their energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.76,0:40:33.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也很感激\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I'm grateful...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.40,0:40:37.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的帮助\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.53,0:40:39.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是从我回到镇上以来的第一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's the first hours passed since I've come back
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.47,0:40:43.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把女巫的事情抛到脑后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}where I haven't thought about witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.98,0:40:47.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想也许我们能过上那样的日子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I supposed one could choose that life...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.71,0:40:53.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,勤恳的工作 和谐的社区 有爱的家庭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}honest work, community, a loving family,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.25,0:40:56.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有女巫的打扰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and not a witch in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.69,0:41:00.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许我们能共同创造这样的生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Maybe there's hope for us yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.13,0:41:02.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.67,0:41:03.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去通知市镇委员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Alert the selectmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.93,0:41:07.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,又发现了一个女巫 跟我走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Another witch has been revealed. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.16,0:41:08.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,又或许不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.63,0:41:11.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,玛丽 西布利\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mary Sibley!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.67,0:41:17.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你丈夫醒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your husband is awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.02,0:41:29.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,乔治醒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}George is awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.19,0:41:30.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,开口说话了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Has he spoken?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.26,0:41:33.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他被人下药 没法开口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He is rendered incapable of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.00,0:41:38.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可不管怎样 我已经知道折磨他的人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nevertheless, the name of his tormentor has been divulged.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.07,0:41:40.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.17,0:41:41.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,被下药 没法开口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}"Rendered unable to speak"?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.97,0:41:45.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你认出了这剂药吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you recognize this potion?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.14,0:41:46.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.58,0:41:48.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是用来止痛的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's a physic for pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.31,0:41:51.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我让以撒喂西布利先生吃的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I gave it to Isaac to give to Mr. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.75,0:41:54.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,止痛用的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A physic for pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.75,0:41:59.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我 区区一剂止痛药\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell me, would a physic for pain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.43,0:42:03.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能让西布利先生没法开口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}seal Mr. Sibley's mouth shut...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:05.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘴里还长出了金色蜘蛛网吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}With a golden web?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.10,0:42:23.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只是止痛剂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A tonic for pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.27,0:42:24.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只此而已\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.54,0:42:27.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,父亲 我想我需要提醒你一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Might I suggest, father,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.61,0:42:30.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利夫人的药只是止痛剂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that Mrs. Sibley's tonic is just that,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.94,0:42:32.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而那张金色蜘蛛网\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and the work of the web is due,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.18,0:42:35.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,更像是真正女巫的杰作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}more likely, to the real witch's spider familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.65,0:42:43.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.15,0:42:45.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是有这种可能 搜查整个房子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's a possibility. Search the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.69,0:42:47.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.89,0:42:50.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.46,0:42:52.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是说蜘蛛吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Did you say a spider?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.13,0:42:57.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是路易斯家的孩子 曾经被女巫折磨控制过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The Lewis child, once tortured and possessed by witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.47,0:42:59.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可她现在看着气色很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yet now she looks remarkably well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.54,0:43:02.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都是因为西布利夫人的照顾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All due to Mrs. Sibley's kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.74,0:43:04.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她救了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.91,0:43:07.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我当时受尽折磨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was tortured and tormented,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.64,0:43:10.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一心求死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}at the verge of begging for death,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.15,0:43:13.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是玛丽 西布利把我从恶魔手中救出\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and Mary Sibley delivered me from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.38,0:43:16.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也正因此我在犹豫要不要说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Which is why I hesitate to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.25,0:43:18.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你要说什么 姑娘\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What is it you have to say, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.72,0:43:19.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一天早上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The other morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.89,0:43:24.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西布利夫人出去做船舶生意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}when Mrs. Sibley was out on shipping business...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.59,0:43:25.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.65,0:43:29.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我经过了提图芭的房间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I did pass Tituba's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.33,0:43:32.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看到她在做奇怪的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and she was doing the strangest thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.63,0:43:34.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我们 默西 告诉我们你看到了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell us, Mercy. Tell us what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.56,0:43:37.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她拿着一只蜘蛛放在脖子上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She held a spider to her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.06,0:43:40.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.83,0:43:42.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.20,0:43:44.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她好像在喂它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She seemed to feed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.94,0:43:48.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.81,0:43:50.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.89,0:44:05.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我在此宣布 以女巫之名\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I hereby arrest you...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.23,0:44:07.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,将你逮捕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}On the charge of witchcraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.26,0:44:09.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,守卫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.26,0:44:11.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-在 先生  -是的 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, sir. - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.28,0:44:20.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,跟我走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
